articles.title: Indiana conducts first execution in 15 years, puts quadruple killer to death - CBS News
articles.description: An Indiana man, Joseph Corcoran, convicted of killing four people including his brother and his sister's fiancé decades ago was put to death, without any independent witness, marking the state's first execution in 15 years.
